visual.name: infographicDesigner
visual.description: Infographic Designer provides infographic presentation of data. It allows you to easily customize chart marks with rich visual elements (icons, images, texts), so you can turn a standard column chart, bar chart, or card chart into a compelling infographic one. For example, using a single icon or stacked multiple icons to constitute a column or bar, you will get a pictographic style column chart or bar chart. Infographic Designer will help your dashboard or reports to be visually beautiful, quickly understood, and easily remembered. Check out the support site at http://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/project/infonice/ for more information. And send us email: infonice@microsoft.com, if you have any questions, suggestions, and feedback.

Small-Multiple.description: Settings of small multiple layout style.

Max Column Header Height.description: Set the maximum height of column headers.

Max Row Header Width.description: Set the maximum width of row headers.

Min Unit Width.description: Set the minimal width of cell chart.

Min Unit Height.description: Set the minimal height of cell chart.

Max Unit Width.description: Set the maximum width of cell chart.

Max Unit Height.description: Set the maximum height of cell chart.

Max Row Width.description: Set the max count of charts in one row.

Show Header.description: Decide whether to show headers or not.

Show Chart Title.description: Decide whether to show chart titles or not.

Text Color.description: Set the color of the text in headers and chart titles.

Font Size.description: Set the font size of the text in headers and chart titles.

Font Family.description: Set the font family of the text in headers and chart titles.

Show Separators.description: Decide whether to show seperator lines or not.

Min Chart Width.description: Set the minimal width of chart.

Min Chart Height.description: Set the minimum height of chart.

Legend.description: Decide whether to show Legend or not.

MeasureAsSeries.description: Show multiple measures as multiple series.

X-Axis.description: Decide whether to show X-axis or not.

Y-Axis.description: Decide whether to show Y-axis or not.

Decimal Places.description: Decide how many decimal places are used to show the values on the axis.

Grid Line.description: Decide whether to show grid line or not.

Minimum Value as Origin.description: Use minimum value as axis origin.

Format Axis Value.description: Decide whether to format axis value or not.

Format Data Value.description: Decide whether to format data value or not.

Aspect Ratio.description: Set the aspect ratio of each chart.

Top Padding.description: Set the top padding of each chart.

Bottom Padding.description: Set the bottom padding of each chart.

Left Padding.description: Set the left padding of each chart.

Right Padding.description: Set the right padding of each chart.

Axis Text Color.description: Set the color of the text in axis.

Axis Font Size.description: Set the font size of the text in axis.

Axis Font Family.description: Set the font family of the text in axis.
